# IntelliJ HTTP Client examples for technical-interview-demo
# These paths are intended for trusted internal or devops access and are not part
# of the supported external `/api/**` contract.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Technical endpoints - actuator info
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/info
Accept: application/json

### Technical endpoints - actuator health
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

### Technical endpoints - actuator liveness
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/health/liveness
Accept: application/json

### Technical endpoints - actuator readiness
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/health/readiness
Accept: application/json

### Technical endpoints - Prometheus metrics for trusted deployment scraping
# Deployment-scoped endpoint. Use this through a trusted cluster scrape or a deliberate port-forward,
# not as part of the supported external `/api/**` contract.
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/prometheus
Accept: text/plain
